    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000">(-NEW-)&nbsp;&nbsp;Setting a variable, g:AsNeededAutoMake, to something like &quot;ls -1l&quot;, lets AsNeeded keep ANtags and ANcmds up-to-date automatically!<br>(bugfix) Taglist does a quick-loading trick that involved using FuncUndefined autocmds.&nbsp;&nbsp;AsNeeded now defers to taglist instead of issuing a warning.<br>(bugfix) ei=all was inadvertently being left on; thus no autocmds were operational after AsNeeded successfully loaded a function.&nbsp;&nbsp;Fixed!<br>(bugfix) included |'patchmode'| in the SaveSettings() and RestoreSettings() bypass functions<br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
        <td class="roweven" valign="top" nowrap><a href="download_script.php?src_id=5719">AsNeeded.vba.gz</a></td>
    <td class="roweven" valign="top" nowrap><b>13</b></td>
